302
00:21:22,140 --> 00:21:22,740
Exactly.

303
00:21:50,920 --> 00:21:51,299
You...

304
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:52,519
You didn't leave a note

305
00:21:53,259 --> 00:21:54,059
when you added her.

306
00:22:27,279 --> 00:22:29,000
Thought you weren't cooking anymore?

307
00:22:29,359 --> 00:22:30,779
And it's all my favorites.

308
00:22:33,240 --> 00:22:34,119
Go wash your hands.

309
00:22:34,339 --> 00:22:35,079
Eat first.

310
00:22:59,160 --> 00:23:00,079
Where did you go today?

311
00:23:00,319 --> 00:23:00,859
A bar.

312
00:23:04,640 --> 00:23:05,740
To a bar in those clothes?

313
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:06,539
Who are you kidding?

314
00:23:09,279 --> 00:23:10,960
This beef is so gamey.

315
00:23:11,660 --> 00:23:12,680
This is way too salty.

316
00:23:12,940 --> 00:23:13,799
Your cooking has really gone downhill.

317
00:23:26,839 --> 00:23:27,920
I saw you at the car market.

318
00:23:28,859 --> 00:23:30,400
Just drive mine for your vacation.

319
00:23:31,319 --> 00:23:32,380
What made you think of buying a car?

320
00:23:35,519 --> 00:23:36,279
Are you stalking me?

321
00:23:41,700 --> 00:23:42,680
I was there to get the car fixed.

322
00:23:44,519 --> 00:23:46,400
You saw me at the car market,

323
00:23:46,559 --> 00:23:47,920
then you cook for me,

324
00:23:47,920 --> 00:23:49,059
and you're all smiles.

325
00:23:49,400 --> 00:23:50,200
You're trying to fish for info,

326
00:23:50,319 --> 00:23:51,039
seeing when I'll leave.

327
00:23:53,140 --> 00:23:53,799
Chen Yi,

328
00:23:54,220 --> 00:23:55,759
are you actually afraid of me,

329
00:23:55,759 --> 00:23:56,619
or just avoiding me?

330
00:24:01,720 --> 00:24:02,359
So,

331
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:05,059
you never planned on leaving from the start.

332
00:24:06,599 --> 00:24:07,960
I finally made it back.

333
00:24:08,140 --> 00:24:09,359
Of course I'm not leaving so easily.

334
00:24:10,980 --> 00:24:12,240
Miao Jing, we're not kids anymore.

335
00:24:12,240 --> 00:24:12,960
It's not appropriate for us

336
00:24:12,960 --> 00:24:13,240
to live together like this.

337
00:24:13,240 --> 00:24:13,759
Oh, by the way,

338
00:24:13,880 --> 00:24:14,900
The latch on my bedroom window

339
00:24:14,900 --> 00:24:15,700
is broken.

340
00:24:15,700 --> 00:24:16,799
Could you take a look at it?

341
00:24:17,059 --> 00:24:18,480
The bathroom always stinks,

342
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:19,359
it's pretty bad.

343
00:24:19,640 --> 00:24:20,559
Maybe you should do something?

344
00:24:20,920 --> 00:24:21,819
And this sofa,

345
00:24:22,079 --> 00:24:23,299
it digs into me every time I sit down.

346
00:24:23,420 --> 00:24:24,200
Doesn't it bother you?

347
00:24:37,599 --> 00:24:38,079
Boss,

348
00:24:38,079 --> 00:24:38,740
one fried noodles!

349
00:24:39,440 --> 00:24:39,900
Sure thing.

350
00:25:01,600 --> 00:25:06,000
♪What carves♪

351
00:25:06,360 --> 00:25:11,400
♪our crossed yesterdays♪

352
00:25:11,640 --> 00:25:17,240
♪Memories slip away♪

353
00:25:17,240 --> 00:25:21,720
♪we evolve into you and me♪

354
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:30,480
[Cut my finger, come home and do the dishes.]

355
00:26:34,500 --> 00:26:35,420
What relationship?

356
00:26:40,279 --> 00:26:42,319
I still need to see how it goes.

357
00:26:49,380 --> 00:26:49,980
I never said,

358
00:26:49,980 --> 00:26:51,500
I came back for you.

359
00:27:36,700 --> 00:27:37,660
I'm hurt.

360
00:27:42,519 --> 00:27:43,839
I'm not lying,

361
00:27:44,099 --> 00:27:45,119
I am really hurt.

362
00:27:47,319 --> 00:27:48,240
Look, the skin is broken.

363
00:27:50,579 --> 00:27:52,119
Any later, it would've healed.

364
00:27:53,759 --> 00:27:54,380
I'm used to it.

365
00:27:54,700 --> 00:27:55,680
I have high standards.

366
00:28:01,880 --> 00:28:02,700
It's a small town,

367
00:28:03,099 --> 00:28:03,880
no match for Haicheng.

368
00:28:04,480 --> 00:28:06,000
If you feel wronged, just go back.

369
00:28:06,759 --> 00:28:07,579
Don't you worry.

370
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:08,839
I never compromise myself.

371
00:28:44,660 --> 00:28:45,220
Look,

372
00:28:46,000 --> 00:28:47,640
you could just hire a repairman,

373
00:28:47,920 --> 00:28:49,400
but Miao Jing makes you do it yourself.

374
00:28:53,799 --> 00:28:55,160
If she wants to pick a fight, let her.

375
00:28:58,539 --> 00:28:59,259
When I saw her the other day,

376
00:29:00,019 --> 00:29:00,880
I barely recognized her.

377
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:02,079
She's changed so much.

378
00:29:02,779 --> 00:29:03,920
She used to be a sweet angel,

379
00:29:04,079 --> 00:29:04,900
now she's all spikes and leather.

380
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:10,059
Gotta find a way to get her out.

381
00:29:12,259 --> 00:29:13,000
Maybe,

382
00:29:13,519 --> 00:29:14,359
you make an excuse

383
00:29:14,359 --> 00:29:15,559
and stay at my place?

384
00:29:16,519 --> 00:29:17,380
Then I'll find her

385
00:29:17,380 --> 00:29:18,519
a nicer apartment.

386
00:29:19,299 --> 00:29:19,960
Anyway,

387
00:29:20,380 --> 00:29:21,119
just move her out first.

388
00:29:23,819 --> 00:29:24,759
Come on, don't do this.

389
00:29:25,319 --> 00:29:26,319
Not that I mind,

390
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:27,500
but I

391
00:29:27,779 --> 00:29:28,880
have a girlfriend now.

392
00:29:35,039 --> 00:29:35,980
You've

393
00:29:36,359 --> 00:29:37,799
seen way bigger things.

394
00:29:38,380 --> 00:29:39,420
Afraid of her?

395
00:29:39,559 --> 00:29:40,140
That's just.

396
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:46,000
Five yuan.

397
00:30:48,019 --> 00:30:48,539
Miao Jing,

398
00:30:49,680 --> 00:30:50,599
bring me some water.

399
00:31:33,000 --> 00:31:33,420
Yi!

400
00:31:33,859 --> 00:31:34,680
Trouble at the pool hall.

401
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:43,660
What happened?

402
00:31:44,519 --> 00:31:46,000
They did a fire inspection days ago.

403
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:47,599
They said private rooms' vision panels

404
00:31:47,599 --> 00:31:48,799
are off-size.

405
00:31:49,079 --> 00:31:49,920
They demanded to see you.

406
00:31:50,079 --> 00:31:50,839
Or they'll call the cops.

407
00:31:51,460 --> 00:31:52,200
Rocky is at the shop,

408
00:31:52,200 --> 00:31:52,880
losing his mind.

409
00:31:53,880 --> 00:31:55,200
The previous owner

410
00:31:55,200 --> 00:31:56,519
put those panels in.

411
00:31:56,759 --> 00:31:58,099
They've been fine for years.

412
00:31:58,880 --> 00:32:00,200
He's clearly looking for trouble.

413
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:06,079
Miao Jing,

414
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,619
I'm heading out.

415
00:32:51,519 --> 00:32:51,880
Boss.

416
00:32:52,660 --> 00:32:53,019
Boss.

417
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:53,480
Take a seat.

418
00:32:56,700 --> 00:32:57,259
I.

419
00:32:57,940 --> 00:32:58,619
Behave.

420
00:33:19,240 --> 00:33:19,880
Yi.

421
00:33:29,960 --> 00:33:30,599
Yi,

422
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,799
you're a hard man to reach.

423
00:33:33,519 --> 00:33:34,059
How about

424
00:33:35,000 --> 00:33:35,720
a game or two?

425
00:33:36,400 --> 00:33:37,160
We can talk while we play.

426
00:33:48,680 --> 00:33:50,079
Quite a big show today, Gordo.

427
00:33:50,839 --> 00:33:52,039
I doubt you're just here to play.

428
00:33:54,079 --> 00:33:54,779
Straight to the point. I like it.

429
00:33:57,039 --> 00:33:58,240
Then let's skip the small talk.

430
00:33:59,279 --> 00:34:00,920
About that partnership we discussed,

431
00:34:01,599 --> 00:34:02,559
have you thought it over?

432
00:34:05,640 --> 00:34:06,099
I believe

433
00:34:06,099 --> 00:34:07,440
I made myself clear last time.

434
00:34:09,599 --> 00:34:10,440
It's non-negotiable.

435
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:14,059
Don't be so quick to say no.

436
00:34:15,500 --> 00:34:16,400
Now,

437
00:34:17,280 --> 00:34:18,239
about those vision panels,

438
00:34:18,639 --> 00:34:19,800
they're off.

439
00:34:21,380 --> 00:34:22,500
It's no big deal, really.

440
00:34:23,780 --> 00:34:24,559
But,

441
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:25,920
if word gets to the top

442
00:34:27,059 --> 00:34:28,639
fixing that will be a real headache.

443
00:34:30,219 --> 00:34:30,659
Right?

444
00:34:35,460 --> 00:34:36,880
I can take the hit on the vision panels.

445
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:38,679
But, Gordo,

446
00:34:39,440 --> 00:34:40,360
you have your own

447
00:34:40,880 --> 00:34:41,440
messy shit

448
00:34:41,440 --> 00:34:42,480
to cover up.

449
00:34:47,199 --> 00:34:47,679
So,

450
00:34:47,679 --> 00:34:49,280
you prefer the hard way.

451
00:35:02,039 --> 00:35:03,880
You're a lone wolf here.

452
00:35:04,539 --> 00:35:05,340
While we

453
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:06,880
have powerful patrons backing us up.

454
00:35:07,840 --> 00:35:08,679
Why bother?

455
00:35:35,559 --> 00:35:36,119
First,

456
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:38,360
pay for the damage and settle this.

457
00:35:39,420 --> 00:35:40,239
Keep your dirty hands

458
00:35:40,239 --> 00:35:41,280
off my turf.

459
00:35:42,800 --> 00:35:43,440
Second,

460
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:45,920
if you call Fire,

461
00:35:46,460 --> 00:35:47,280
I'll call Management.

462
00:35:48,619 --> 00:35:49,860
Neither of us is gonna have it easy.

463
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:54,619
And third,

464
00:35:56,039 --> 00:35:57,099
You know

465
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:59,480
I can get real nasty.

466
00:36:01,300 --> 00:36:02,719
Easy! Don't do anything stupid!

467
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,199
Don't you know

468
00:36:04,739 --> 00:36:05,400
who's

469
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:06,460
backing me up?

470
00:36:12,019 --> 00:36:12,679
All I know is

471
00:36:12,679 --> 00:36:13,360
your heart is

472
00:36:13,360 --> 00:36:14,460
racing too fast.

473
00:36:19,739 --> 00:36:20,480
Take it easy, please.

474
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,480
Well, well.

475
00:36:22,559 --> 00:36:23,500
Quite a party here.

476
00:36:24,139 --> 00:36:25,320
Mr... Mr. Zhang!

477
00:36:25,980 --> 00:36:27,079
Save me! Help!

478
00:36:34,539 --> 00:36:35,179
So this is

479
00:36:35,179 --> 00:36:36,480
the big shot behind you.

480
00:36:45,000 --> 00:36:45,699
Give me a hand.

481
00:36:45,820 --> 00:36:46,460
Help me up!

482
00:36:52,840 --> 00:36:53,679
Remember to pay up.

483
00:37:01,039 --> 00:37:02,440
I called to invite you,

484
00:37:02,719 --> 00:37:03,599
but you wouldn't come.

485
00:37:04,739 --> 00:37:05,639
Just happened to be passing by,

486
00:37:07,340 --> 00:37:08,099
so I dropped in to see you.

487
00:37:12,000 --> 00:37:12,599
Just passing by,

488
00:37:15,139 --> 00:37:16,699
then my little shop is truly honored.

489
00:37:23,239 --> 00:37:24,280
Are you interested in

490
00:37:24,900 --> 00:37:25,420
a game of pool?

491
00:37:27,079 --> 00:37:27,920
I sprained my wrist.

492
00:37:28,019 --> 00:37:28,659
Can't play.

493
00:37:43,059 --> 00:37:43,500
Fine.

494
00:37:44,480 --> 00:37:44,940
I won't disturb you then.

495
00:37:45,599 --> 00:37:46,280
Let's go, Li.

496
00:38:18,760 --> 00:38:19,320
Boss,

497
00:38:19,619 --> 00:38:21,000
what's wrong with that pool hall?

498
00:38:21,000 --> 00:38:21,539
Did they get into trouble?

499
00:38:22,699 --> 00:38:23,340
The owner of that place

500
00:38:23,599 --> 00:38:24,199
grew up around here.

501
00:38:24,199 --> 00:38:25,039
He's a regular thug.

502
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:26,320
I heard that before

503
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,320
he went off to do business.

504
00:38:27,320 --> 00:38:28,500
No news from him for years.

505
00:38:28,739 --> 00:38:29,659
He only came back recently.

506
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,000
Where did he go?

507
00:38:31,460 --> 00:38:32,380
Who knows?

508
00:38:32,760 --> 00:38:33,940
Probably didn't strike it rich.

509
00:38:34,539 --> 00:38:35,400
Otherwise, why would he return?

510
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,719
Still living like a thug,

511
00:38:37,099 --> 00:38:38,360
just hole up here in the old town.

512
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:46,059
Everyone gets a paid day off today.

513
00:38:46,199 --> 00:38:47,179
Go home and get some good rest.

514
00:38:49,619 --> 00:38:50,519
What's with the faces?

515
00:38:50,519 --> 00:38:51,360
Not happy about a vacation?

516
00:38:51,360 --> 00:38:52,179
Move it! Move it! Quick!

517
00:38:52,420 --> 00:38:53,119
Don't hold me up from closing.

518
00:38:53,679 --> 00:38:54,219
Let's go! Move it!

519
00:38:54,219 --> 00:38:54,980
Hurry up!

520
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,380
Are you hurt anywhere else?

521
00:39:04,059 --> 00:39:04,619
No, that's it.

522
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:05,699
I'm fine, Yi.

523
00:39:19,880 --> 00:39:20,880
Disinfect it yourself later.

524
00:39:22,199 --> 00:39:22,719
Don't worry.

525
00:39:30,159 --> 00:39:31,000
Bo, Bo,

526
00:39:31,300 --> 00:39:32,059
I spotted a woman

527
00:39:32,059 --> 00:39:32,940
snooping around over there.

528
00:39:33,119 --> 00:39:33,780
Could she be with...

529
00:39:34,179 --> 00:39:34,659
It's fine, it's fine.

530
00:39:34,659 --> 00:39:35,420
Time to clock out. Go, go.

531
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:39,659
Looks nice.

532
00:39:47,019 --> 00:39:47,739
Then I'll head back first.

533
00:39:49,079 --> 00:39:49,719
Call me if anything comes up.

534
00:39:49,960 --> 00:39:50,519
Sure. Bye.

535
00:39:50,679 --> 00:39:51,039
Bye.

536
00:40:20,099 --> 00:40:20,800
You're back.

537
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:22,820
Here.

538
00:40:52,840 --> 00:40:54,579
When did you return to Vineton?

539
00:40:58,619 --> 00:40:59,480
Why do you ask?

540
00:41:01,719 --> 00:41:02,940
I just thought of how,

541
00:41:03,320 --> 00:41:04,599
when you were at Company Kuang,

542
00:41:04,599 --> 00:41:05,679
you used to follow Zhang Bin.

543
00:41:06,300 --> 00:41:08,019
How come you seem distant now?

544
00:41:11,860 --> 00:41:13,139
I left Zhang Bin back then.

545
00:41:16,300 --> 00:41:17,039
Is that so?

546
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:18,840
Then for the past two years

547
00:41:19,179 --> 00:41:20,039
who were you with?
